        CHARGING IS A SNAP.
      </h3>
      <img src="{{ 'triggle_pixel-d.svg' | asset_url }}" class="{{titleDecoMy}}">
      <p class="{{descSize}} swiper-no-swiping">
        With the built-in "X" charging contact structure and magnet array, the iPad mini 6 case allows you
        to snap your iPad mini 6 onto the 
        <a class="text-cyan" href="/collections/pitaflow-for-tablets">Pita!Flow Charger</a>
        to auto-align for fast and stable wireless charging-like experience.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full sm:w-5/9 lg:w-5/8">
      <picture>
        <source data-srcset="{{'casepro-ipad-mini6-section3-1.webp' | asset_url}}" media="(min-width: 1280px)">
        <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}" data-src="{{'casepro-ipad-mini6-section3-1-s.webp' | asset_url}}"
          alt="{{ altName }}" class="block w-full lazyload">
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="{{wClass}} {{pdClass_b}}">
  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row-reverse justify-between items-center">
    <div class="w-full sm:w-2/5 lg:w-3/10 mb-10 sm:mb-0">
      <h3 class="{{titleSize}} swiper-no-swiping">
        GET MORE OUT OF YOUR DEVICE.
      </h3>
      <img src="{{ 'triggle_pixel-d.svg' | asset_url }}" class="{{titleDecoMy}}">
      <p class="{{descSize}} swiper-no-swiping">
        MagEZ Case Pro for iPad mini 6 offers more than protection and style.
        To help you get the most out of the productive tool, we built the 
        <a class="text-cyan" href="/collections/pitaflow-for-tablets">Pita!Flow for Tablets</a> system. 
        You can snap the device to the Pita!Flow Charger to enjoy a cable-free charging experience. 
        Or mount and charge it wirelessly on our 
        <a class="text-cyan" href="/products/magez-charging-stand">MagEZ Charging Stand</a>, 
        so you can make your iPad mini computer-like to get your work done or simply enjoy gaming and reading more.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full sm:w-5/9 lg:w-5/8">
      <picture>
        <source data-srcset="{{'casepro-ipad-mini6-section3-2.webp' | asset_url}}" media="(min-width: 1280px)">
        <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}" data-src="{{'casepro-ipad-mini6-section3-2-s.webp' | asset_url}}"
          alt="{{ altName }}" class="block w-full lazyload">
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- comment -%}
