  <div class="{{wClass}}">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-stretch">
      <div class="swiper-container content-slider w-full sm:w-2/5 lg:w-3/10 mb-10 sm:mb-0">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
          <div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h3 class="{{titleSize}} swiper-no-swiping">
              CHARGING IS A SNAP.
            </h3>
            <img src="{{ 'triggle_pixel-d.svg' | asset_url }}" class="{{titleDecoMy}}">
            <p class="{{descSize}} swiper-no-swiping">
              With the built-in "X" charging contact structure and magnet array, the iPad mini 6 case allows you
              to snap your iPad mini 6 onto the 
              <a class="text-cyan" href="/collections/pitaflow-for-tablets">Pita!Flow Charger</a>
              to auto-align for fast and stable wireless charging-like experience.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h3 class="{{titleSize}} swiper-no-swiping">
              EXTREME CONVENIENCE.
            </h3>
            <img src="{{ 'triggle_pixel-d.svg' | asset_url }}" class="{{titleDecoMy}}">
            <p class="{{descSize}} swiper-no-swiping">
              MagEZ Case Pro for iPad mini 6 is built to work seamlessly with the 
              <a class="text-cyan" href="/collections/pitaflow-for-tablets">Pita!Flow Charger</a> and 
              <a class="text-cyan" href="/products/magez-charging-stand">MagEZ Charging Stand</a>.<br>
